<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Verse</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/style.css" />
  </head>
  <body class="bg-gray-50">
    <%- include("partials/header.ejs") %>


    <div class="relative h-96 w-full overflow-hidden">
      <img
        decoding="async"
        src="https://framerusercontent.com/images/QUC1DPYvY9k6q9wes1rKIadFOFY.png"
        alt="getting started with verse"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover object-center"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-800/90 to-purple-800/90">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center h-full text-center px-4">
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4 animate-fade-in-up">
            Getting Started
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/90 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            What you need to know to get started with Verse
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>


    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out transform hover:-translate-y-1 cursor-pointer">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">What is Verse?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Verse is a blogging platform designed to let you create, view, and delete your blog posts with ease. 
            It's a place to share your thoughts, make notes, and keep track of your insights. Whether you're a 
            hobbyist or a professional, Verse provides a seamless and fun experience to express your creativity.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out transform hover:-translate-y-1 cursor-pointer">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">How can I use Verse?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Using Verse is simple! Just start writing. You can create new blog posts by adding titles and content, 
            view them in a clean layout, and delete any outdated posts. The platform allows you to manage your 
            content effortlessly—everything you need is at your fingertips!
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out transform hover:-translate-y-1 cursor-pointer">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">What makes Verse different?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Verse offers an intuitive and minimalist interface that allows you to focus on your writing without distractions. 
            Unlike other platforms, Verse emphasizes simplicity—giving you the freedom to create, manage, and delete posts 
            easily while keeping your workflow smooth and efficient.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out transform hover:-translate-y-1 cursor-pointer">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Is Verse free to use?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Yes! Verse is completely free to use for anyone who wants to share their ideas, stories, or notes. 
            There are no hidden fees or paid plans, so you can start blogging right away.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out transform hover:-translate-y-1 cursor-pointer">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Need technical skills?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Not at all! Verse is designed for everyone, whether you're a tech-savvy blogger or a beginner. 
            The user-friendly interface makes it easy for anyone to start writing, managing, and sharing 
            their content with just a few clicks.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out transform hover:-translate-y-1 cursor-pointer">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">View others' posts?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Currently, Verse focuses on individual blogging with private posts. However, future updates will 
            include features to explore other users' content and connect with the blogging community!
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <%- include("partials/footer.ejs") %>

    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
  </body>
</html>